der 15") in order to make it clearer that this code denotes something other than age 1. Users are cautioned that this may have an effect on any analyses performed using these variables.;Subject: Study Level Error Note, Notes: Users are advised that some DATOS-A publications exclude data from two sites that had low response rates. However, the public use files include data from all six sites.;Subject: Study Level Error Note, Notes: <p>DATOS-A is an ongoing collaborative research effort of the National Development and Research Institutes at North Carolina (NDRI), Texas Christian University, the University of California at Los Angeles, and NIDA. For additional information, see the DATOS Web site
